data.description: Welcome to luxury living in beautiful Warm Springs! This magnificent 5 bedroom, 5.5 bath home is set on 3.93+/- acres of pristine land, featuring a stunning pool that beckons relaxation and entertaining in style. Built by Rock n' Roll Hall of Fame and Country Music Hall of Fame, Chip Moman, this meticulously designed home embodies a perfect blend of style and comfort. This home boasts an open floor plan seamlessly connecting living spaces. With a double island kitchen, sleek granite countertops, tile backsplash, and a built in gas grill, this is a culinary chef's dream! Indulge in the home's master retreat! This spacious master bedroom transitions to an elegant master bath adorned with beautiful tile, double vanities, a separate shower and a relaxing soaking tub - a sanctuary of relaxation! With the additional bedrooms and full baths, this is perfect for families or guests. These comfortable rooms ensure comfort and convenience for everyone! Step outside into your very own backyard oasis! A sparkling saltwater pool is complimented by a large pool house featuring a wet bar and wine cellar - the epitome of outdoor living. For the homeowner who enjoys both convenience and adventure, this property is a dream come true! Ample storage meets RV/boat parking, providing the perfect balance for those with a passion for both a well-organized home space and freedom to explore! This one will go quick! Give The Charles Davis Team a call today to schedule an appointment and get more information!
